item.description: × HD Wallpaper ❮ ❯ Scholars and thinkers from all over the world gather at the city of Antoinerei. It is here where the commonly overlooked Digger lives. Many don't give a second look to Digger due to his small frame, until they come upon his researches in chronoscience. Digger loves clocks, he believes that within these little mechanical toys lies many more yet to be discovered secrets. Through the use of his "Time Nest" Digger can control the flow of time.
